&lt;p&gt;QphoX is looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Production Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to join our Engineering team in developing and manufacturing advanced electro-optical systems for quantum computing applications. To achieve our mission, we are seeking a hands-on engineer with strong assembly, testing, and production skills who enjoys working in a fast-paced, multidisciplinary environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Joining a dynamic team of engineers, scientists, and technicians, you will play a key role in transforming innovative quantum technologies into reliable products. You will work at the intersection of optics, electronics, mechanics, and manufacturing, helping to scale cutting-edge hardware from prototype to production.&lt;/p&gt;
