&lt;li&gt;BSc degree in Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Mechatronics, Applied Physics, Manufacturing Engineering, or a related technical field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-5 years of experience in manufacturing, assembly engineering, production engineering, or electro-mechanical assembly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with precision assembly, PCB Soldering, testing, and troubleshooting of complex hardware systems.&lt;/li&gt;
